snippet.title: there's this girl - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Play on iOS (https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/theres-this-girl/id1444002032), Android (https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.AngelaHe.TheresThisGirl), or web (https://zephyo.itch.io/theres-this-girl)!

Experience love between two earnest stargazers, still searching for their path in life. 

The future is unclear: Will their dreams be broken? Will they walk different paths? And.. can their love be torn apart?

there's this girl Github: https://github.com/zephyo/there-s-this-girl
Facebook: https://facebook.com/zephybite 
Tumblr: http://zephyo.tumblr.com 
Twitter: https://twitter.com/zephybite 

Music
vowl. - imagine (feat. shiloh)
Alembic - i fall in love, too easily

-----
heyyo frends, long time no post, school is difficult as usual! but i made another thing during another game jam, worked on it in thanksgiving break, and here it is. ty for watching and i hope yall like it :3
